            <fr:taxon>Corollary</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {U}\in \mathcal {V}]]></fr:tex> is an impredicative pair of universes, then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {U}]]></fr:tex> is reflective in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {V}]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
 
   
